Got a fix for this.  I'm waiting to hear back from [@Claw](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/100668-claw/) as to whether it's a bug in KSP or not, so this may change, but if you put the following into a file called

KWPatch-fairings.cfg

in the GameData\KW-Rocketry-Community-Fixes directory, the fairings will work:

    @PART[KW2mFairingPF|KW5mFairingPFE|KW3mFairingPFE|KW1mFairingPFE|KW2mFairingPFE|KW3mFairingPF|KW1mFairingPF|KW2mFairingPF]
    {@MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]{	@nSides = 64	nCollidersPerArc = 4}
    }
